ase</span><hr size=1> I'm not sure exactly where to post this, so I'll post this here and one other spot.<br>
<br>
Hi, I'm starting an Enchanter and I'm NOT going to twink him. People have told me that twinking casters isn't a good idea, and I want to try to do things all on my own again (the very first time I played the game was the funnest time).<br>
Since I've been playing a warrior and shaman for most of my EQ life, I need help. I need to know a few things...<br>
<br>
1. For the first few spell circles, what are the best spells to buy?<br>
<br>
2. I'm starting an Erudin Enchanter that worships Prexus, will I have any faction problems?<br>
<br>
3. Where's a good place to hunt to start to get better armor than cloth?<br>
<br>
4, I've never been an Erudite either, how long can I stay on the Erudin continent to level?... Which leads to my next question..<br>
<br>
5. Where's a good spot to hunt near Erudin? I don't want to stray too far from my hometown.<br>
<br>
If you could add any additional information I would be very grateful. I've had a problem finding Enchanter only sites..<br>
<br>
-Chris <br>
