        Erudin is a bad place to hunt.  I suggest you take the first boat to qeynos and get out of there.  (when in qeynos you will not be able to purchase tiny daggers to summon pets, but who cares?  your lvl 1 pets suck any way.)  i suggest you buy only shallow breath and the defense spell and chill at qeynos till about 5. (buy your lvl 4 spells in qeynos, all of them.)  now that your LVL five walk to the south karanas by follow the shore of the river in west karanas(to avoid danger).  once in south karanas beg or buy a tele to Steamfont.  Horay! steamfont will be able to supply you tiny daggers and spells from ak'anon.  hunt here till about 15. <br>
<br>
          You may notice that the Enchanters guild does not sell pet spells past lvl 4.  your right.  you will have to get all you pet spells in HHK from now on. yes, it does blow.<br>
<br>
     Well take my word or ignore it.  I have taken this path and has served me quite well.<br>
<br>
<br>
